VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT \.Append\(.*HttpContext\.Current\.Request\.Url
WHEN EXPR MISSING:(Uri\.EscapeDataString|UrlEncode|IsLocalUrl|allowlist|whitelist)
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects the usage of untrusted URL concatenation using the Append method, which may lead to security vulnerabilities.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Untrusted URL Concatenation: Append Method.
